description:
Ariel X, aka "The Assassin", returns for season 5. She finished 9th last season and improved every match. She is smooth, tough and a good smack talker. The Assassin knows how to punish losers in RD4.

Welcome Gwen Diamond aka "The Tornado", this 20 year old from Kansas thinks she tough and has what it takes to be successful here at Ultimate Surrender, only time will tell..

This match has it all, crushing leg body scissors, submissions, head scissors, face sitting and fingering. Throw in some great chin locks and hardcore kissing, and you end up with a great match up.
title: The Assassin(2-2) Not Ranked
